To compile the code:
$ icc *.cpp -o res -mkl

To compile the code with OpenMP:
$ icc *.cpp -o res -mkl -fopenmp


System parameters available to the program:
n:      number of particles
d:      linear number of sectors (total d^2)
l:      domain size
tmax:   total time
dt:     time step size
kT:     total energy
g:      drag coefficient
m:      mass
sigma:  WCA potential parameters
eps:    WCA potential parameters

To change the parameters, edit "init" file.